title: Thirumana Porutham Marriage Horoscope Matching
description:
Apps Arasan presents Thirumana Porutham/ marriage matching App a completely free app and it can be use offline app.
Marriage is considered and celebrated as important tradition and culture in India. Marriage is made to make a bond and good relationship between man and woman. In ancient period to follow the virtue the marriage has been made by our ancestors. Marriage matching horoscope in India are made between wedlock man and woman which makes them a best couple to make love, to bring unity in the family, to follow the tradition, to develop good generation, to improve financial status and to make a healthy life. There are many components to marriage: self-respect, selflessness, communication, forgiveness, honesty and enduring to the end.
The jathagam porutham application has 10 porutham marriage horoscope and marriage compatibility tester. Marriage matching and marriage tradition are made by matching birth horoscopes which is now-a-days termed as marriage matching horoscope.
There is a proverb saying that “Marriages are made in heaven”. This proverb indirectly says us to make the wedding life, a heaven. In general, to make a better life marriage matching is made on the basis of stars between man and woman.
In our Thirumana porutham app contains all rasi star matching for both man and women marriage life.  We are detailed about the 12 Rasi porutham with content.
Thirumana Porutham app Host Feature:
Available all Rasi with Star porutham.
More information available about marriage matching.
Offline mode. Enjoy the app without internet access
Have a quick view on the historical facts of the day by using the widget.
Simple UI and Easy to use.

title: এশিয়া কাপ ২০১৮/Asia cup 2018
description:
আসছে ১৫ সেপ্টেম্বর থেকে সংযুক্ত আরব আমিরাতে শুরু হচ্ছে এশিয়া কাপের এবারের আসর। এশিয়ার পাঁচটি টেস্ট খেলুড়ে দলের পাশাপাশি প্লে-অফ থেকে একটি দল খেলবে এবারের আসরে।
এবারের আসরটি এশিয়া কাপের ১৪তম আয়োজন। আসরের উদ্বোধনী ম্যাচেই মাঠে নামবে বাংলাদেশ। ১৫ সেপ্টেম্বর দুবাইয়ে অনুষ্ঠিতব্য ম্যাচটিতে বাংলাদেশের প্রতিপক্ষ শ্রীলঙ্কা।
আর ফাইনাল ম্যাচ অনুষ্ঠিত হবে ২৮ সেপ্টেম্বর। বাংলাদেশ, ভারত, পাকিস্তান, শ্রীলঙ্কা ও আফগানিস্তানের পাশাপাশি অংশ নেবে বাছাইপর্ব পেরনো আরও একটি দল।

title: Gigwalk
description:

Gigwalk is changing the future of work by enabling people to find jobs in their area whenever and wherever it is most convenient to them. To become a Gigwalker, simply download the app! title: Circuit
description:
Use our latest smart-scan technology - and pay for your laundry with your phone.
Make doing the laundry less of a hassle with a mobile app that's as easy-to-use as our washing machines and dryers! The Circuit Laundry app lets you top up your Circuit app account* in seconds, and then you're good to go...just turn up at your nearest Circuit launderette, load your laundry, scan a machine's QR code and select the programme you want to start - job done! Your credit will be adjusted automatically so you'll always have your circuit account balance to hand. No need to stay and watch your washing.
Once the washer or dryer gets going the app also gives you a countdown** that tells you how long there is to go until your laundry is done.
* Please note that your Circuit app account is separate to your laundry card account you access from the Circuit website. If you haven’t used the Circuit app before you will need to sign up separately on the app. Balances from your laundry card cannot be transferred to your Circuit app account and vice versa.
**The app will rely on your phone having a wi-fi, 3G or 4G signal inside the laundry room to activate the machines - and also to see the countdown on the cycle if you leave to do something else while your wash completes. As long as you're connected, you can see how long is left on your chosen cycle and get on with other things instead of waiting in the launderette.
By downloading this app, you agree to the following T&C's:
You accept that you have a non-exclusive licence to use the app. You agree not to copy the app or infringe our intellectual property rights in the app.
The minimum amount of top-up credit you can buy is £5.00. Your payment will be processed through PayPal and Circuit will not hold any card details.
You can apply for a refund of part-used top-up credit by emailing us at apprefund@circuit.co.uk with details of registered email address, the date of the in-App purchase, the amount of credit purchased, and the amount of credit to be refunded. No refund will be given on balances of less than £5.00. Refunds will incur an administration charge of £3.00, which will be deducted directly from the refund value. Refunds will be made using the payment method used for the purchase. No refund will be processed for any free credit. Unused credits will expire 12 months after the date of purchase. Please see our website www.circuit.co.uk for more information.

title: Angel Number Signs
description:
Try this app for free for 7 days!
The Angels favorite way to communicate with us is through Angel signs, and numbers are one of their favorite mediums. Every number has its own inherent meaning and energetic vibration. The Angels love to deliver numbers, repeated multiple number patterns such as 11, 22, 33, 44 and number sequences such as 1234 as a means to bring you guidance and reassurance. This app will assist you to understand the messages that you are seeing on a daily basis. The Angels can deliver a number sign to you in many ways such as on a clock, computer, your phone, on a sign, house number, in a book, on your shopping docket, in a song plus they love to draw your attention to car number plates too. The means in which numbers are presented is endless and synchronicity plays a huge part in the Angelic orchestration of the numbers appearance.

title: Small Goal - Habit Tracker & Goals Reminder, To do
description:
KEYWORDS: to do, change, good habits, habit, habits, good habits, habit tracker, daily checklis, daily tracker, goal, goal tracker, goals, golas planner, goals app, goals on track, task, tasker, tasker app, task manager, list, daily, to do list, task list, planner, calender, reminders, strides
▌Small Goal
• By establishing a scientific and effective plan, you are constantly reminded, motivated and guided to action.
• A combination of small goals will help you lose weight, exercise, reduce anxiety, increase energy and productivity.
• The ultimate goal is to gradually improve and get some healthy habits, cut some bad habits. let you become better and better!
▌How Small-Goal works
• Select and set goals
• Remind and try to complete and record the goals
• Track data and trends, and constantly adjust to the best implementation plan
• Achieve your goal and move on to the next challenge
• Keep your passion and state alive, get habits
▌Functionality
• Quick selection habit, without tedious addition
• goals reminder and recorder
• goals execution data statistics and analysis report
• Cloud backup, data not lost
▌Future features
• Individualized implementation plan, quantified and simplified
• Adopt the ingenious method of easier action
• Customized services, professional guidance, AI tracking
• Scientific programs from the psychological and physiological research rooms of famous universities
• Invite friends to compete and motivate each other
• Everyone is a supervisor, encourage your growth and progress
▌Habits
• Habits are no more than routines which you perform subconsciously. To build one - train yourself. To break one, find another one which is similar, yet different and nicer, and repeat it until it sticks.
• To assist you with this Small-Goal lets you set reminders for each habit and displays them on days when you need to be successful. This is especially useful if you have a to do list with repeating tasks or if you want to be reminded to do the same thing every day. It can also be used as a calendar planning tool or checklist, but also as a very effective repeating reminder (e.g. to drink water every 2 hours).
• Small-Goal does feel a little like a game in which you compete with yourself. The task is to get a long streak for the habit you are working on by covering your goals. The longer the better. It takes a couple of months to fully build a new routine, so don't give up - it takes time and if you are consistent it will work; even if it takes a few attempts.
• There are many things which you may want to improve. Small-Goal can be used as a planner in building habits like taking your pills regularly, exercise, or keep to a diet. It can also be used as a helper for people suffering from memory problems. As for your vices, Small-Goal can be a useful goal tracking tool, or a smart notebook, to assist you while breaking bad habits like nail-biting, drinking alcohol and even improving your dating skills.
• It is entirely up to you, really. But why not give it a try and have a convenient helper on the go?

\xe2\x80\xa2 Habits are no more than routines which you perform subconsciously. To build one - train yourself. To break one, find another one which is similar, yet different and nicer, and repeat it until it sticks.
\xe2\x80\xa2 To assist you with this Small-Goal lets you set reminders for each habit and displays them on days when you need to be successful. This is especially useful if you have a to do list with repeating tasks or if you want to be reminded to do the same thing every day. It can also be used as a calendar planning tool or checklist, but also as a very effective repeating reminder (e.g. to drink water every 2 hours).
\xe2\x80\xa2 Small-Goal does feel a little like a game in which you compete with yourself. The task is to get a long streak for the habit you are working on by covering your goals. The longer the better. It takes a couple of months to fully build a new routine, so don't give up - it takes time and if you are consistent it will work; even if it takes a few attempts.
\xe2\x80\xa2 There are many things which you may want to improve. Small-Goal can be used as a planner in building habits like taking your pills regularly, exercise, or keep to a diet. It can also be used as a helper for people suffering from memory problems. As for your vices, Small-Goal can be a useful goal tracking tool, or a smart notebook, to assist you while breaking bad habits like nail-biting, drinking alcohol and even improving your dating skills.
\xe2\x80\xa2 It is entirely up to you, really. But why not give it a try and have a convenient helper on the go?"

description:
Download this App and listen to Holy Quran recitation of surah al baqarah offline on your mobile device.
Application Features:
With app you can do the following:
- Listen to surah albaqarah mp3 OFFLINE. You will find sheikh Sudais, Sheikh Mishary Rashid Al Afasy, Sheikh Maher Al Muaiqly, Sheikh Abdurrahman Al Ausy and Sheikh Abdulbasit Abdussamad voices. They all play without internet connection.
The surah al baqarah is the longest surah in the Holy Quran and reciting it more upon, drives away Jinn from the place it is recited. It is of significant important to listen more upon to this surah al baqarah or even memorize its verses.
- Read surah al Baqarah in Arabic Text (check screenshots of this app)
- You can read and listen at the same time.
- Read Sheikh Muhammad Metwali Al-Sha'raawi Tafseer of surah albaqarah offline verse by verse from verse one to verse two hundred and eighty six. The tafseer is in Arabic text.
- Check prayer times and more.
The following reciters are available:
Sheikh abdelrahman al sodes
sheikh abdul basit abdus samad
sheikh mishary rashid alafasy
Sheikh Maher al muaiqly
Sheikh Abdurrahman al ausy (alossi surah baqarah mp3).
Download this App if you want to listen to The Holy Quran Recitation of Surah albaqarah offline on your mobile device.
The Cow or Sūrah al-Baqarah (Arabic: سورة البقرة‎, "The Cow") is the second and longest chapter (Surah) of the Qur'an. It consists of 286 verses, 6201 words and 25500 letters. It is a Mediniite surah, that is to say that it was revealed at Medina after the Hijrah, with the exception of a few verses which Muslims believe was revealed during the last Hajj of prophet Muhammad (pbuh), the Farewell Pilgrimage.
This is the longest Surah in the Quran. It was the first Surah to be revealed at Medina, but different verses were revealed at different times, covering quite a long period so much so that the verses with regard to riba (interest or usury) were revealed in the final days of prophet Muhammad (pbuh), after the conquest of Makkah (Maariful Quran).
The verse 281 in Surah Baqarah, is the last verses of the Quran to be revealed, this happened on the 10th of Dhul al Hijjah 10 A.H., when prophet Muhammad was in the course of performing his last Hajj, and only eighty or ninety days later he died (Qurtubi).
Surah al-Baqarah enjoins fasting on the believer during the month of Ramadan.
It is the longest Surah in the Qur’an and was revealed over a long period. It is a Mediniite Surah dealing with the Hypocrite (Munaafiqeen) and injunctions pertaining to various matters.
It includes many verses which have virtues like the first four and last three verses and the special Verse of the Throne (Aayatul Kursi). Prophet Muhammad is reported to have said,
“Do not turn your houses into graves. Verily, Satan does not enter the house where Surat Al-Baqarah is recited.” [Muslim, Tirmidhi, Musnad Ahmed]
Ad-Darimi also recorded that Ash-Sha`bi said that `Abdullah bin Mas`ud said, "Whoever recites ten Ayat from Surat Al-Baqarah in a night, then Shaytan will not enter his house that night. (These ten Ayat are) four from the beginning, Ayat Al-Kursi (255), the following two Ayat (256-257) and the last three Ayat.
Notable verses:
Verse 255 is "The Throne Verse" (آية الكرسي ʾāyatu-l-kursī). It is the most famous verse of the Qur'an and is widely memorized and displayed in the Islamic world due to its emphatic description of God's omnipotence in Islam.
Verse 256 is one of the most quoted verses in the Qur'an. It famously notes that "there is no compulsion in religion". Two other verses, 285 and 286, are sometimes considered part of "The Throne Verse".
Apart from the surah al bakarah many more surahs are available in my catalog. Just search for kareemtkb and you'll see all my apps.

Thank you very much foe checking out this surah bakarah mp3 app!

মেয়েদের বিভিন্ন ধরনের লাইফস্টাইল ও ফ্যাশন টিপস নিয়ে কথা বলা হয়েছে তারা কীভাবে দৈনন্দিন জীবনে চলাফেরা করবে কীভাবে জীবন গড়বে, কীভাবে নিজেকে আকর্ষণীয় করে তুলবে, কীভাবে আকর্ষণীয়  ফিগার  করে তুলবে আরও মেয়েদের সম্পর্কে বিভিন্ন টিপস নিয়ে আলোচনা করা হয়েছে । আমাদের এই অ্যাপ দ্বারা আমরা চেষ্টা করেছি মেয়েদের সব রকম স্টাইল ও ফ্যাশন বিষয়ক টিপস এবং সাজেশন দেয়ার

title: صور حرف M مزخرفة 💖💖 2018‎ - بدون نت
description:
صور حرف M مزخرفة 2018‎ بدون انترنت
في هذا التطبيق تناسب كل الاذواق منها ما هو رومانسى , كارتونى , بالخط العربى الجميل لصور حرف M
كما يحتوي التطبيق على ما يلي : أحلي صور حرف M لكل الأسماء التي تبدأ بحرف M نقدم لكم كولكشن صور وخلفيات مميزة بحرف الإم "M" شيك جدا في تصميماتها ومختلفة الأشكال لتناسب مختلف أذواقكم.
صور حرف M مزخرفة 2018‎ توفر لكم تحديث جديد يضم أجمل صور حروف مزخرفة مرتبة حسب الحروف
- اكثر من 500 حرف M ناري وحرف وردي وحرف مزخرف وحرف احترافي.
- اسمك بأحرف من نار و اسمك بأحرف من ذهب و اسمك في سلسلة من ذهب .
- صورحروف مزخرفه رومانسية جميلة مع الحروف
- يمكنك تحميل صور حروف مزخرفه لجهازك بالضغط على زر حفظ اعلى الصورة.
- إمكانية مشاركة صور حروف مزخرفة والمحتوى عن طريق تطبيقات التواصل الاجتماعي.
صور حروف مزخرفة و اسمك بأحرف من ذهب و اسمك بأحرف من نار
صور وخلفيات للتحميل وغيرها في تطبيق الحرف المزخرف والمزخرف الاحترافي للحروف.
تطبيق الحرف الناري يشمل مجموعة رائعة ومميزة من الاحرف المكتوبة بلون وشكل النار.
هنا في هذا التطبيق يمكنك كتابة اسمك بالحرف الناري ورؤية اسمك وهو يلمع كالنار.
زين حروف اسمك بالنار، واحصل على زخرفة اسمك بشكل رائع وجميل .
باستطاعتك رسم حروف اسمك من نار وزخرفة حروفك المفضلة .
يمكنك ارسال الحرف الناري لاشخاص تحبهم ، سيكونو سعيدين بذلك جدا ، حمل التطبيق ولن تندم .
يمكنك حفظ الحرف الناري لاسمك على موبايلك الخاص كي تتمتع برؤية حروف اسمك بشكلها الرائع والمثير والجذاب كلما أحببت .
شارك اصدقائك هذا التطبيق ولا تحرمهم من رؤية حروف اسمائهم من نار.
بإمكانكم مشاركة الصور مع كثير من برامج التواصل الإجتماعي مثل: فيسبوك، تويتر ، واتس أب، فايبر، تانجو، وغيرها.
تطبيق ذو واجهة سهلة وبسيطة للمستخدم .
تطبيق اسمك باحرف من نار هدية لكم بعد نجاح تطبيق الحرف الذهبي والمسمى اكتب اسمك بأحرف من ذهب .

title: Bhagavad Gita Quotes
description:
The Bhagavad Gita (Sanskrit pronunciation:lit. "The Song of God"), often referred to as the Gita, is a 700 verse Hindu scripture in Sanskrit that is part of the Hindu epic Mahabharata (chapters 23–40 of the 6th book of Mahabharata).
The Gita is set in a narrative framework of a dialogue between Pandava prince Arjuna and his guide and charioteer Lord Krishna. Facing the duty as a warrior to fight the Dharma Yudhha or righteous war between Pandavas and Kauravas, Arjuna is counselled by Lord Krishna to "fulfill his Kshatriya (warrior) duty as a warrior and establish Dharma". Inserted in this appeal to kshatriya dharma (chivalry) "is a dialogue ... between diverging attitudes concerning methods toward the attainment of liberation (moksha)".
The Bhagavad Gita presents a synthesis of the concept of Dharma, theistic bhakti, the yogic ideals of moksha  through jnana, bhakti, karma, and Raja Yoga (spoken of in the 6th chapter) and Samkhya philosophy.
This app contains:
Image quotes from Bhagavad Gita option to Set-picture-as but also Photo Sharing
Bhagavad Gita Quote Videos
Bhagavad Gita Text Quotes
Bhagavad Gita Audio
Bhagavad Gita Video
A More Spiritual Life
Life Lessons
The Bhagavad Gita's call for selfless action inspired many leaders of the Indian independence movement including Bal Gangadhar Tilak and Mahatma Gandhi. Gandhi referred to the Gita as his "spiritual dictionary".

Gautam Buddha | Gautam Buddha Worship | Gautam Buddha Photo Frame | Gautam Buddha Photo Frame | Biography of Gautam Buddha In Marathi
The word Buddha means "awakened one" or "the enlightened one". "Buddha" is also used as a title for the first awakened being in a Yuga era. In most Buddhist traditions, Siddhartha Gautama is regarded as the Supreme Buddha of the present age. Gautama taught a Middle Way between sensual indulgence and the severe asceticism found in the śramaṇa movement common in his region.
The teachings of the Buddha are known as Buddhism. Buddhism is mostly about ending the feeling of pain that all people feel inside. Gautama Buddha taught that pain is a part of all life. He taught that pain is because of desire. And he showed that there is a way to end desire and end pain by doing good things, not doing bad things, and training one's mind. This is done to end pain and gain enlightenment.

The word Buddha means "awakened one" or "the enlightened one". "Buddha" is also used as a title for the first awakened being in a Yuga era. In most Buddhist traditions, Siddhartha Gautama is regarded as the Supreme Buddha of the present age. Gautama taught a Middle Way between sensual indulgence and the severe asceticism found in the \xc5\x9brama\xe1\xb9\x87a movement common in his region.

The teachings of the Buddha are known as Buddhism. Buddhism is mostly about ending the feeling of pain that all people feel inside. Gautama Buddha taught that pain is a part of all life. He taught that pain is because of desire. And he showed that there is a way to end desire and end pain by doing good things, not doing bad things, and training one\'s mind. This is done to end pain and gain enlightenment.
